Tummblr Ligher
https://github.com/ryhmrt/tumblrlighter

Copyright (c) 2011 Ryohei Morita, Keisuke Chiba

Introduction
  This is a Chrome extension it prevents Tumblr Dashboard
  being huge size when using AutoPatchWork.

Usage
  Simply add this extension to your Chrome.
  Then, open your Tumblr dashboard.
  This extension will remove some top entries from your
  bashboard to purge some memory when you deep page exploring.

